      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.wFTC0sGqdpnZUib4]{Gear Boost}</p>\n<p>When wielding weapons with the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.Nrf6oy9pJwcEmryP.JournalEntryPage.nXkFsyxk7Vybdn7G#archaic]{Archaic} weapon special property, the damage you deal is never reduced as a result of that property. Archaic weapons you wield gain @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.O5GDQUKPCJ9Zbnfj.JournalEntryPage.zOJ86MDq6kNzAAbB#bleed]{Bleed} 1d8 as a critical hit effect (Core Rulebook 182). If the weapon already has a critical hit effect, when you score a critical hit, you can apply either the weaponâ€™s normal critical hit effect or this bleed effect. The bleed damage increases by 1d8 at 11th level and every 4 soldier levels you have beyond 11th (maximum bleed 4d8 at 19th level).</p>"
